WEBVTT

00:07.600 --> 00:08.920
‎SAY NO TO PIRACY, SUPPORT ORIGINALS

01:37.800 --> 01:41.600
ADAPTED FROM XI XING’S NOVEL
<i>QUEEN CHU</i> ON QIDIAN.COM

01:46.040 --> 01:47.120
WANGCHENG

01:47.200 --> 01:49.760
Hooray!

01:49.840 --> 01:52.720
-Your Highness!
-Your Highness!

01:52.800 --> 01:57.760
-Your Highness!
-The Grand Princess!

01:57.840 --> 02:00.400
Your Highness, we've prepared wine.

02:00.480 --> 02:03.120
Do me the honor.
Have some victory wine before you go.

02:03.960 --> 02:05.320
I appreciate it, General,

02:05.400 --> 02:07.520
but we must hurry to Yunzhong. No delays.

02:08.199 --> 02:09.160
Your Highness.

02:10.080 --> 02:13.520
She longs to go home.
Don't stand in her way.

02:17.240 --> 02:19.320
Everybody, thank you for all this.

02:19.400 --> 02:21.200
Your Highness, take this for the journey.

02:21.280 --> 02:23.360
-Your Highness.
-Folks, the army will move out.

02:23.440 --> 02:26.080
Don't stand in their way or delay them.

02:26.160 --> 02:27.120
We appreciate your good intentions.

03:16.640 --> 03:17.880
My Lord, Mr. Deng is here.

03:22.280 --> 03:24.360
-Show him in.
-Yes.

03:31.320 --> 03:34.400
Mr. Xie, you're working at this late hour.

03:34.480 --> 03:36.600
You truly are a pillar of the court.

03:36.680 --> 03:38.920
You didn't visit me so late

03:39.000 --> 03:40.680
just to praise me, did you?

03:41.640 --> 03:43.440
I'm here to congratulate you.

03:44.640 --> 03:45.480
Mr. Xie,

03:46.160 --> 03:49.720
the battle of Wangcheng was a good one.

03:49.800 --> 03:51.360
What makes you say that?

03:52.400 --> 03:54.880
Her Highness commanded the victory.

03:54.960 --> 03:56.320
And of course,

03:57.120 --> 03:59.080
my brother fought valiantly.

03:59.160 --> 04:01.000
I dare not take any credit.

04:01.080 --> 04:03.720
Xie Yanlai escorted Her Highness

04:04.320 --> 04:07.280
and helped secure
the victory of Wangcheng.

04:07.880 --> 04:10.400
So, he's likely to take over

04:10.480 --> 04:12.600
the frontier troops in Yunzhong.

04:13.360 --> 04:14.400
Mr. Xie,

04:15.400 --> 04:16.800
that was a clever plan.

04:19.920 --> 04:21.320
Have you lost your senses?

04:21.399 --> 04:25.280
His Majesty made Yanlai
the Imperial Guard Commander.

04:25.960 --> 04:27.680
How could he leave the imperial city?

04:28.280 --> 04:29.360
Besides,

04:30.120 --> 04:32.160
it won't be easy
to take over frontier troops.

04:32.240 --> 04:34.440
It might be hard for someone else.

04:34.520 --> 04:36.520
But for you,

04:37.160 --> 04:38.480
it's a piece of cake.

04:40.400 --> 04:42.000
After all, your brother

04:42.080 --> 04:45.160
deployed the bandits
from Cangmu Stronghold to fight for him.

04:46.880 --> 04:49.720
I just wonder if he knows

04:50.520 --> 04:52.840
his connections with those bandits

04:52.920 --> 04:55.720
in the Wei Village.

04:55.800 --> 04:59.000
Mr. Deng, what's said

05:00.160 --> 05:02.600
can't be unsaid.

05:05.600 --> 05:08.960
Mr. Xie, don't be nervous.

05:09.560 --> 05:11.520
I'm just curious.

05:11.600 --> 05:15.640
Who actually set the fire
in the Wei Village?

05:16.600 --> 05:18.760
And why does a man

05:18.840 --> 05:22.280
who cares for his younger brother
refuse to see the truth?

05:22.360 --> 05:24.320
If you had proof,

05:24.400 --> 05:26.480
you could report it to His Majesty.

05:26.560 --> 05:28.880
Instead, you came to probe me so late.

05:29.480 --> 05:31.240
Let me give you some advice.

05:31.320 --> 05:33.000
You can't bring down my clan

05:33.080 --> 05:35.520
by using Xie Yanlai.

05:36.120 --> 05:38.080
There's a reason

05:38.160 --> 05:41.280
that my clan has endured for a century.

05:42.000 --> 05:44.880
I'm just talking about the facts.

05:49.160 --> 05:51.600
As for your century-old authority…

05:52.480 --> 05:54.360
Handled properly,

05:55.440 --> 05:57.960
even a big tree can be uprooted.

06:04.480 --> 06:06.120
How interesting.

06:07.600 --> 06:10.240
Mr. Deng, how about

06:11.240 --> 06:12.760
we make a bet?

06:19.960 --> 06:20.800
On what?

06:20.880 --> 06:22.840
Tomorrow,

06:24.120 --> 06:25.960
we'll both plead illness to avoid court.

06:26.560 --> 06:29.000
-See what His Majesty will do?
-No.

06:29.080 --> 06:33.400
I want you to see
who the ministers will support

06:34.760 --> 06:36.520
and how much

06:37.680 --> 06:39.480
my clan matters.

06:39.560 --> 06:40.680
All right.

06:43.320 --> 06:44.920
I'll take that bet.

07:01.480 --> 07:03.360
The Northern Desert envoy is here.

07:04.640 --> 07:05.760
You promised

07:06.600 --> 07:09.520
that you would send troops
to help us invade Wangcheng.

07:09.600 --> 07:10.920
But instead of sending any troops,

07:11.000 --> 07:13.920
you watched our defeat and heavy losses.

07:14.000 --> 07:17.880
My remaining troops all died in Yunzhong!

07:18.800 --> 07:21.640
I wonder how you'll explain that.

07:22.400 --> 07:24.440
Battle conditions change rapidly.

07:25.600 --> 07:29.080
I did my best to let you pass through

07:29.160 --> 07:31.160
at great personal risk.

07:32.000 --> 07:33.720
How could I have foreseen everything?

07:34.760 --> 07:35.920
Besides,

07:36.000 --> 07:38.720
if your remaining troops

07:38.800 --> 07:40.600
died in my prefecture,

07:40.680 --> 07:43.240
the court would suspect and blame me.

07:44.040 --> 07:45.760
It wouldn't benefit me at all.

07:47.480 --> 07:48.800
If it makes you

07:49.400 --> 07:52.200
suspect my sincerity in allying with you,

07:55.160 --> 07:56.720
I'll be really disappointed.

08:01.760 --> 08:03.480
Do you think this excuse

08:04.280 --> 08:08.160
will justify my troops dying in vain?

08:16.800 --> 08:19.040
Has your king ever trusted me?

08:20.280 --> 08:24.040
After all, he still hasn't told me

08:24.920 --> 08:26.800
why he asked me to help your men

08:27.320 --> 08:30.840
set the fire in the Wei Village
five years ago.

08:32.600 --> 08:34.919
If I hadn't sent men to clear it up,

08:35.760 --> 08:38.159
it wouldn't have been kept
so perfectly secret.

08:39.120 --> 08:41.000
But now, you doubt me.

08:44.440 --> 08:46.520
Go back and tell your king.

08:47.080 --> 08:49.560
A plan succeeds through mutual trust.

08:50.920 --> 08:52.880
If he demands an answer on this matter,

08:55.680 --> 08:57.000
our alliance will end here.

09:51.560 --> 09:53.600
Jiu, had a nightmare?

09:58.160 --> 10:01.160
Just now, you looked in pain.

10:03.160 --> 10:04.080
Nothing.

10:06.640 --> 10:07.680
Just a dream.

10:14.080 --> 10:15.960
I'm going to see my father soon.

10:19.680 --> 10:21.240
Aren't you supposed to be happy?

10:23.240 --> 10:25.120
It's not that I'm not happy.

10:26.280 --> 10:27.640
I'm just scared.

10:29.640 --> 10:30.760
Of what?

10:32.240 --> 10:33.680
My father's illness.

10:38.720 --> 10:40.440
People get sick.

10:42.480 --> 10:44.920
Don't worry. Maybe

10:45.640 --> 10:49.960
by the time we arrive,
your father will have recovered.

10:53.480 --> 10:55.440
I hope so.

12:01.040 --> 12:05.440
THE GREAT BORDER GATE

12:22.800 --> 12:25.360
The General once said,
when you came back someday,

12:25.440 --> 12:26.800
he would be waiting at the city gate.

12:31.960 --> 12:35.080
<i>Yeah. You're the undefeated God of War.</i>

12:35.160 --> 12:37.440
<i>You're the esteemed Guard General.</i>

12:37.520 --> 12:40.560
<i>But have you ever asked</i>
<i>if I wish to be a general's daughter?</i>

12:41.280 --> 12:42.480
Since childhood,

12:43.080 --> 12:45.760
other girls have had parents around.
What about me?

12:45.840 --> 12:47.840
I've always been neglected.

12:48.600 --> 12:50.960
Have I ever cried or complained to you?

12:51.040 --> 12:53.360
I've never dared
to ask you for a little concern

12:53.440 --> 12:54.880
because you've always been busy.

12:54.960 --> 12:57.480
You're busy protecting frontier people.

12:57.560 --> 12:59.600
You're busy forging your fame.

12:59.680 --> 13:01.200
You're too busy

13:01.280 --> 13:04.640
to ask your daughter
what she really wants!

13:07.120 --> 13:09.800
Father, Xun and I love each other.

13:09.880 --> 13:11.280
What's wrong with his origin?

13:11.920 --> 13:13.320
If I can't marry him,

13:13.400 --> 13:14.800
why did you marry my mother,

13:14.880 --> 13:16.320
a noble young lady from far away?

13:16.400 --> 13:18.840
She stayed with you
and wasted her life here.

13:18.920 --> 13:21.320
Your mother… You have no right to judge.

13:21.400 --> 13:23.160
Then don't interfere with mine!

13:25.640 --> 13:26.800
<i>Sorry.</i>

13:27.400 --> 13:29.040
<i>I'm sorry, Father.</i>

13:30.280 --> 13:31.200
<i>Father.</i>

13:32.080 --> 13:33.680
I'm sorry!

14:03.680 --> 14:04.600
Father,

14:07.120 --> 14:08.520
I'm finally back.

14:08.600 --> 14:09.600
Good.

14:12.000 --> 14:13.600
Good you're back.

14:35.360 --> 14:37.200
When did this happen?

14:37.280 --> 14:38.720
How did your eyes…?

14:41.400 --> 14:42.720
What did the Army Physician say?

14:44.480 --> 14:46.640
We can send for an Imperial Physician.

14:46.720 --> 14:48.160
You'll be cured.

14:48.240 --> 14:49.800
Don't bother.

14:50.400 --> 14:53.040
With or without my eyesight,

14:53.120 --> 14:56.480
I can see everything in the camp.

14:58.320 --> 14:59.880
It's all in my heart.

15:13.160 --> 15:14.520
Actually,

15:16.840 --> 15:19.120
after I lost my sight,

15:20.600 --> 15:21.800
I finally managed

15:23.160 --> 15:24.960
to find inner peace.

15:26.320 --> 15:27.720
I feel I am getting old.

15:29.960 --> 15:31.880
I often thought of the past.

15:34.520 --> 15:37.000
The more I thought,
the more I felt sorry for you.

15:37.600 --> 15:39.200
You've grown up,

15:40.920 --> 15:43.880
and I've never flown kites with you.

15:45.160 --> 15:47.080
I even missed

15:49.280 --> 15:50.560
your coming-of-age ceremony.

15:52.400 --> 15:54.200
I still remember those words you said

15:55.320 --> 15:56.960
when you left here.

15:57.800 --> 15:59.680
In the dead of night,

16:01.720 --> 16:04.160
it has haunted me all this time.

16:06.440 --> 16:07.560
You were right.

16:08.440 --> 16:10.720
I've never been a good father.

16:13.400 --> 16:15.520
I've never asked

16:17.480 --> 16:19.360
what you really want.

16:20.600 --> 16:21.840
I have no right

16:24.280 --> 16:26.120
to beg for your forgiveness.

16:28.840 --> 16:32.240
Don't say that, Father.
I'm sorry for what I did to you.

16:33.640 --> 16:37.640
Father, I shouldn't have said
those harsh words.

16:39.240 --> 16:41.720
Five years ago, I shouldn't
have left willfully

16:41.800 --> 16:43.480
without even leaving you a message.

16:45.720 --> 16:46.720
Father,

16:48.920 --> 16:50.480
will you forgive me?

16:52.720 --> 16:55.080
I've never blamed you.

16:55.720 --> 16:57.160
There's nothing to forgive.

16:58.240 --> 17:00.320
When you're no longer so stubborn,

17:00.400 --> 17:02.560
it feels strange to me.

17:03.560 --> 17:05.119
The biggest pride

17:06.079 --> 17:08.200
of my life

17:09.319 --> 17:11.359
isn't defeating enemies,

17:13.520 --> 17:15.160
but having a daughter

17:18.000 --> 17:20.440
even more stubborn than I am.

17:25.839 --> 17:27.680
On the day of Wangcheng victory,

17:28.359 --> 17:30.360
joy overwhelmed me.

17:31.760 --> 17:33.160
I asked Changrong to write

17:35.440 --> 17:37.360
a congratulatory poem on my behalf.

17:46.120 --> 17:48.160
<i>My precious daughter was too confined</i>

17:48.240 --> 17:50.560
<i>To let her talents shine</i>

17:51.880 --> 17:54.120
<i>How could I not think of her?</i>

17:54.200 --> 17:56.520
<i>Yet she chose to temper herself</i>

17:56.600 --> 17:59.120
<i>She left home and achieved great deeds</i>

17:59.200 --> 18:01.080
<i>And her talents finally shone brightly</i>

18:01.160 --> 18:03.320
<i>Glorious and bright</i>

18:03.400 --> 18:05.840
<i>Her light reaches the whole land</i>

18:06.720 --> 18:09.560
Your Majesty, an urgent military report
about rewards

18:09.640 --> 18:11.000
came from Wangcheng.

18:11.720 --> 18:13.280
Without His Majesty's approval,

18:13.360 --> 18:15.520
Her Highness distributed rewards
on her own.

18:16.120 --> 18:18.000
Wasn't she overstepping her authority?

18:24.000 --> 18:25.680
Mr. Xie is on sick leave.

18:26.480 --> 18:27.560
Mr. Deng has a day off, too.

18:28.280 --> 18:31.120
To whom shall we send
this military report?

18:31.840 --> 18:34.080
Mr. Deng, of course.

18:34.680 --> 18:37.040
The late Emperor made him the regent.

18:37.120 --> 18:39.320
We can't bypass him in military affairs.

18:39.400 --> 18:40.800
Military affairs are urgent.

18:40.880 --> 18:42.760
Mr. Deng knows nothing
about warfare tactics.

18:42.840 --> 18:45.000
Before Mr. Xie asked for sick leave,

18:45.080 --> 18:47.800
he ordered that all military reports
to be sent to him.

18:48.960 --> 18:51.320
Mr. Deng also gave an order.

18:51.400 --> 18:54.560
Frontier affairs must be reviewed by him.

18:55.160 --> 18:58.280
The Xie Clan of Gaoyang
has stood for a century.

18:58.360 --> 19:00.240
Oh. My memory fails me.

19:00.840 --> 19:02.160
How many prime ministers

19:02.240 --> 19:04.440
have come from their clan?

19:06.840 --> 19:10.200
Since the founding of our dynasty,
there have been six.

19:13.880 --> 19:15.440
Then send it to Mr. Xie.

19:17.920 --> 19:20.080
-But…
-This is ridiculous.

19:21.880 --> 19:23.080
Anything else?

19:23.160 --> 19:25.160
Then the court is dismissed.

19:25.240 --> 19:27.920
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty.
-We bid farewell to Your Majesty.

19:29.760 --> 19:31.680
XIE RESIDENCE

19:34.160 --> 19:35.400
Mr. Xie, have you heard?

19:35.480 --> 19:37.960
In today's court, we won decisively.

19:38.040 --> 19:39.920
I heard that old censor

19:40.000 --> 19:41.640
nearly fainted from anger.

19:42.560 --> 19:44.200
How many times have I warned you?

19:45.080 --> 19:47.480
You must not be so arrogant.

19:47.560 --> 19:49.840
Arrogance leads to misfortune.

19:49.920 --> 19:52.480
When people praise you
and our Xie household,

19:52.560 --> 19:53.720
it's hard for me to stay humble.

19:54.480 --> 19:55.800
I can't help feeling proud.

19:57.440 --> 19:58.480
Forget it.

19:59.560 --> 20:02.160
Mr. Xie, won't you review the report?

20:02.960 --> 20:04.800
Send this report to Mr. Deng.

20:05.400 --> 20:06.840
To him?

20:07.560 --> 20:08.880
Won't you review it?

20:10.840 --> 20:13.920
No one but Mr. Deng
can review this report.

20:14.480 --> 20:16.200
What if he doesn't…?

20:18.760 --> 20:19.840
He will.

20:43.920 --> 20:44.800
Mr. Deng,

20:47.640 --> 20:49.160
you lost.

20:51.920 --> 20:52.920
Don't be angry.

20:53.520 --> 20:56.560
You need patience when dealing
with Xie Yanfang.

20:57.160 --> 21:00.520
He got the military report,
but didn't even bother to review it.

21:01.320 --> 21:03.400
He's obviously humiliating me.

21:13.920 --> 21:14.760
This man…

21:29.960 --> 21:30.840
It's him.

21:31.960 --> 21:33.920
-Who?
-Liang Qiang.

21:34.520 --> 21:36.400
The Third Prince's case
involves his family.

21:36.480 --> 21:38.240
Xie Yanfang had him exiled.

21:41.240 --> 21:42.400
Very good.

21:48.400 --> 21:51.760
APPROVED

21:52.840 --> 21:53.920
Approving it already?

21:56.600 --> 21:58.640
Since he's Xie Yanfang's enemy,

21:59.760 --> 22:01.800
I'll give him some support.

22:04.080 --> 22:05.440
SEAL OF THE GRAND MENTOR

22:12.160 --> 22:13.720
IMPERIAL SEAL OF THE CHU EMPEROR

22:15.000 --> 22:18.280
Father. Father, are you asleep? I'm back.

22:19.600 --> 22:22.800
I got it. I'm still awake.
I was waiting for you.

22:29.840 --> 22:33.160
Father, guess what I brought back.

22:36.080 --> 22:38.200
Did my patrol lady

22:39.480 --> 22:40.840
bring back a spy?

22:46.680 --> 22:48.360
I brought back a rabbit.

22:49.080 --> 22:50.440
Well done, Zhao.

22:51.360 --> 22:56.360
Jiu didn't catch it for you, did he?

22:58.160 --> 22:59.680
No.

22:59.760 --> 23:02.520
Father. Look.

23:02.600 --> 23:05.480
This little rabbit looks like a snowball.

23:06.720 --> 23:08.240
Rabbits can bite.

23:09.000 --> 23:10.240
Don't forget.

23:10.840 --> 23:14.000
You got bitten when you were little
and cried for three days.

23:16.520 --> 23:17.520
I did?

23:19.880 --> 23:21.640
I don't remember at all.

23:22.360 --> 23:23.720
You remember almost nothing

23:25.840 --> 23:27.160
about your childhood.

23:34.680 --> 23:36.120
In your childhood,

23:37.360 --> 23:38.640
you were extraordinary.

23:39.360 --> 23:41.000
When you were born,

23:42.160 --> 23:43.560
the room was bathed in red light.

23:44.720 --> 23:46.840
A fortune teller passed by

23:47.880 --> 23:49.880
and was utterly shocked.

23:50.640 --> 23:51.760
He pointed at you and said,

23:52.880 --> 23:54.400
"She's blessed by heaven."

23:57.120 --> 23:59.840
Really? Did you

24:00.440 --> 24:03.080
go out again and hear
a story at the tea house?

24:03.680 --> 24:06.640
What happened next in the story?

24:06.720 --> 24:08.040
Later,

24:08.760 --> 24:10.960
at this girl's first birthday,

24:12.400 --> 24:15.520
she grabbed the Frontier Tally.

24:17.360 --> 24:19.200
When she was five,

24:20.400 --> 24:23.960
she led the servants and maids

24:24.560 --> 24:27.000
to use brooms as spears

24:28.840 --> 24:30.720
and pot lids as shields,

24:31.960 --> 24:36.040
and she has piled up an enemy city

24:38.000 --> 24:39.480
with bamboo steamers.

24:40.320 --> 24:41.440
She even learned

24:42.240 --> 24:44.440
to deploy troops.

24:44.520 --> 24:46.520
In the end, she captured

24:47.440 --> 24:51.320
the steward's three hens
that would still lay eggs.

24:56.480 --> 24:59.680
I don't remember that.
Was I that remarkable?

25:00.680 --> 25:02.440
Yes, you were.

25:03.120 --> 25:04.400
And the old steward

25:05.520 --> 25:07.320
cried for two nights.

25:17.960 --> 25:20.640
Father, I love the congratulatory poem

25:22.480 --> 25:23.800
you wrote for me.

25:25.880 --> 25:27.960
Let me recite it again.

25:33.920 --> 25:35.640
<i>My precious daughter was too confined</i>

25:37.600 --> 25:39.360
<i>To let her talents shine</i>

25:40.560 --> 25:42.240
<i>How could I not think of her?</i>

25:44.520 --> 25:46.280
<i>Yet she chose to temper herself</i>

25:47.360 --> 25:49.280
<i>She left home and achieved great deeds</i>

25:50.880 --> 25:52.720
<i>And her talents finally shone brightly</i>

25:55.080 --> 25:56.960
<i>Glorious and bright</i>

25:58.480 --> 26:00.280
<i>Her light reaches the whole land</i>

26:02.520 --> 26:05.000
Father. Father!

26:07.040 --> 26:10.200
Father! Army Physician!

26:11.640 --> 26:12.520
Father.

26:27.960 --> 26:29.640
When I left five years ago,

26:30.800 --> 26:32.480
Father could still draw bows and shoot.

26:34.720 --> 26:36.640
When did he fall ill?

26:38.440 --> 26:39.960
Let me be honest.

26:40.720 --> 26:43.960
Over the past two years,
the General has been growing weaker.

26:50.040 --> 26:53.520
Actually, whether he did or didn't disarm,

26:54.240 --> 26:55.800
he'd end up the same.

26:56.520 --> 26:58.360
He's been poisoned for three years.

26:59.320 --> 27:01.760
<i>You sent him those cakes yourself.</i>

27:01.840 --> 27:04.720
<i>From the Capital to Yunzhong,</i>

27:04.800 --> 27:06.040
<i>they were delivered monthly.</i>

27:06.120 --> 27:06.960
CHU MANSION

27:07.040 --> 27:08.920
<i>Chu Ling would be killed anyway.</i>

27:09.520 --> 27:11.240
<i>Not only by my blade,</i>

27:12.200 --> 27:14.120
<i>but also by his daughter's love.</i>

27:14.200 --> 27:15.240
<i>This is impossible.</i>

27:15.920 --> 27:18.720
<i>In my past life, poisoned jujube cakes</i>

27:18.800 --> 27:20.720
<i>were sent to my father after my wedding.</i>

27:21.640 --> 27:23.240
<i>But in this life, no cakes were sent.</i>

27:24.200 --> 27:25.800
<i>Why is Father still ill?</i>

27:27.520 --> 27:30.320
Do you know what happened to my father?

27:31.520 --> 27:33.240
I'm not sure about the reason.

27:34.600 --> 27:35.960
I'll make him some medicine

27:36.040 --> 27:38.120
for refreshment and replenishment.

27:44.000 --> 27:45.520
You served him for five years.

27:45.600 --> 27:48.000
Do you know why he's fading so quickly?

27:50.400 --> 27:51.360
Sorry.

27:53.000 --> 27:54.280
I have no idea.

28:08.920 --> 28:10.400
In this new life,

28:13.480 --> 28:15.040
nothing has changed.

28:17.320 --> 28:19.680
For you, something has.

28:29.160 --> 28:32.720
Yet some regrets are inevitable.

28:41.360 --> 28:43.280
Everything has its destiny.

28:46.120 --> 28:47.240
So does a human.

28:49.280 --> 28:51.040
He's defended the frontier all his life,

28:52.440 --> 28:54.120
and people revere him.

28:54.880 --> 28:56.240
In the final days of his life,

28:59.480 --> 29:00.840
his daughter and brothers-in-arms

29:02.520 --> 29:03.560
keep him company.

29:05.320 --> 29:06.320
Perhaps,

29:07.600 --> 29:09.400
he isn't in that much pain.

29:12.680 --> 29:15.040
Even if he passes away,

29:18.120 --> 29:19.640
his love for you

29:21.800 --> 29:23.280
won't fade away.

29:24.120 --> 29:25.640
But he shouldn't be like this.

29:26.920 --> 29:28.280
He just shouldn't.

29:29.160 --> 29:30.840
He kills enemies at the frontier

29:31.960 --> 29:33.760
and protects people here.

29:36.000 --> 29:38.200
He has done everything
a general should do.

29:40.040 --> 29:41.960
He protects 200,000 soldiers

29:42.560 --> 29:44.840
and secures the peace of the state.

29:50.960 --> 29:51.960
What else do you want?

29:52.040 --> 29:53.760
I want him to live.

29:54.360 --> 29:55.760
I want him to live!

29:55.840 --> 29:57.400
I want him to call me "silly girl",

29:57.480 --> 30:00.840
make jujube cakes with me,
and teach me riding and archery!

30:01.960 --> 30:03.320
I want to make it up

30:03.960 --> 30:05.640
and do what a daughter should do.

30:07.920 --> 30:10.880
I want him to wait for me
to come home even if he scolds me.

30:12.160 --> 30:15.800
I don't want a cold memorial tablet
of the Guard General.

30:28.640 --> 30:31.400
GATEWAY OF CANGMU STRONGHOLD

30:38.000 --> 30:39.400
What's wrong, Aunt?

30:41.000 --> 30:42.120
Chu Ling.

30:42.200 --> 30:44.080
CHU LING'S LIFE BURNS LOW.
BEYOND ALL HEALING. PLEASE REPLY SOON

30:45.120 --> 30:46.600
He's dying.

30:50.960 --> 30:52.960
Aunt, you…

30:54.000 --> 30:55.000
Are you going to see him?

31:37.680 --> 31:38.600
Jiu.

31:40.960 --> 31:42.000
Tell me.

31:43.000 --> 31:44.400
What will a man think

31:45.880 --> 31:46.840
before he dies?

31:54.400 --> 31:55.800
Words left unsaid,

31:57.640 --> 31:58.960
promises left unfulfilled…

32:01.080 --> 32:02.240
Or…

32:03.360 --> 32:04.400
wishes that went unmet.

32:06.400 --> 32:08.040
What could be

32:09.880 --> 32:11.000
my father's wish?

32:13.080 --> 32:14.200
If you really want to know,

32:15.200 --> 32:18.640
you can ask him when he wakes up.

32:20.160 --> 32:22.120
Just stop torturing yourself.

32:28.560 --> 32:29.400
Zhao,

32:32.880 --> 32:35.160
you look like you did something wrong.

32:36.400 --> 32:38.320
Your father wouldn't like it.

32:40.000 --> 32:41.760
I just want to figure it out.

32:44.920 --> 32:46.480
What exactly went wrong

32:47.680 --> 32:49.880
that made me end up like this again?

32:51.480 --> 32:53.720
I have tried so hard.

32:53.800 --> 32:55.520
I have tried everything.

32:55.600 --> 32:57.560
Why will my father still leave me?

33:00.880 --> 33:03.200
Zhao, calm down.

33:03.800 --> 33:05.440
What else can I do?

33:05.520 --> 33:09.520
Tell me. What else can I do
to save my father?

33:32.480 --> 33:35.840
MIGHT AND RIGHT

33:48.800 --> 33:50.560
It still tastes a bit bland.

33:53.560 --> 33:55.360
He can't take Zhuyu Powder.

33:55.440 --> 33:57.040
He's too weak to take it now.

33:59.960 --> 34:01.960
Madam Ge? You…

34:02.960 --> 34:04.320
Why are you here?

34:06.440 --> 34:07.960
I'm your father's…

34:12.239 --> 34:13.520
old friend.

34:14.600 --> 34:15.679
I'm here for his final farewell.

34:23.280 --> 34:24.480
Who on earth are you?

35:02.400 --> 35:03.600
Old friend?

35:04.880 --> 35:06.360
What kind of friend

35:07.120 --> 35:09.560
would even remember his food taboos?

35:13.880 --> 35:15.800
She didn't fight like ordinary bandits.

35:16.920 --> 35:18.240
In the Wangcheng battle,

35:19.040 --> 35:20.600
the way she wielded twin blades

35:22.200 --> 35:23.040
was peculiar.

35:26.720 --> 35:28.520
Mu Mianhong, head of Cangmu Stronghold,

35:29.280 --> 35:30.800
mastered twin scimitars.

35:30.880 --> 35:33.720
In the first year of Tianshu
when Father suppressed them,

35:34.240 --> 35:35.440
she jumped off a cliff and died.

35:37.560 --> 35:39.320
Could she be…?

35:43.320 --> 35:44.520
Mu Mianhong.

35:57.440 --> 36:00.840
General, this is our new maidservant.

36:00.920 --> 36:02.400
She can't speak,

36:02.480 --> 36:06.000
but she's good at decoction and soup.

36:07.760 --> 36:08.800
Thanks for your work.

36:55.800 --> 36:57.040
Thank you.

37:55.080 --> 37:56.720
WE SWEAR THIS LOVE AND MATRIMONY
BEFORE HEAVEN, EARTH AND OUR ANCESTORS

37:56.800 --> 37:58.800
BREAK THIS OATH AND WE BE CURSED
BY CHU LING, MU MIANHONG

38:00.880 --> 38:02.880
<i>Do you like this kind of father?</i>

38:03.600 --> 38:04.800
No?

38:06.240 --> 38:07.080
Why?

38:07.160 --> 38:09.320
Because he's a hero to others.

38:09.840 --> 38:11.760
He's a hero to people in Yunzhong.

38:12.440 --> 38:15.680
But I want him to be an ordinary father.

38:16.640 --> 38:20.160
He would carve wooden dolls for me,
watch fireworks with me,

38:21.000 --> 38:23.200
give me pretty braids,

38:24.720 --> 38:28.200
and be there with me
for every important moment.

38:29.440 --> 38:30.440
But actually…

38:31.280 --> 38:32.400
none of this happened.

38:34.000 --> 38:34.840
What about…

38:37.600 --> 38:38.760
your mother?

38:42.880 --> 38:45.240
Could Father have been lying all along?

38:46.600 --> 38:47.760
My mother is…

38:49.800 --> 38:50.640
It can't be.

39:04.360 --> 39:06.600
JOY AND HEALTH FOREVER

39:09.080 --> 39:10.120
Zhao.

39:12.920 --> 39:14.240
Zhao.
